data.description: ACERAGE PLUS LOCATION! With 2.54 acres this beautiful ranch style home is composed of a little over 1,800 square foot right outside the heart of Adairsville! Just 10 minutes to Downtown Adairsville and 15 minutes to the center of Calhoun you couldn't ask for a better slice of heaven so close to your normal amenities and school systems! Whip up a wonderful home cooked meal in your new kitchen with stainless steel appliances, cozy up on your couch next to the warm gas logged fireplace, or sip your morning coffee on the screened in back porch and watch the wildlife all around. This home is a wonderful floorplan suitable for all needs. It hosts the master on the main level with an oversized spare bedroom, 2 wonderful full piece bathrooms, updated countertops, ceramic tile flooring, and 2 extra storage sheds for all the husbands/wives that have a knack for collecting extra tools and supplies! Don't miss your opportunity. Schedule your showing today!
